#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Testing authentication to a separate OIDC-like server can be tricky.\n"
"Quarkus offers several options, from mocking to running a local OIDC provider."
msgstr "测试独立的类 OIDC 服务器的身份验证可能比较棘手。Quarkus 提供了多种选择，从模拟到运行本地 OIDC 提供程序。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
